### SimpleMDB API Test – REST Client (VS Code)
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:5000
@resource = api/v1/items
@itemId = 1

### -------------------------------------------------
### CREATE (POST)
### -------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{resource}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample Item",
  "description": "Created via REST Client",
  "price": 10.5
}

### -------------------------------------------------
### READ (GET by ID)
### -------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{resource}}/{{itemId}}
Accept: application/json

### -------------------------------------------------
### UPDATE (PUT)
### -------------------------------------------------
PUT {{baseUrl}}/{{resource}}/{{itemId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Item",
  "description": "Updated via REST Client",
  "price": 12.0
}

### -------------------------------------------------
### DELETE (DELETE)
### -------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{resource}}/{{itemId}}
Accept: application/json

### -------------------------------------------------
### LIST (GET with pagination)
### -------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{resource}}?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json
